## How to Run

### 1. Train a Decision Tree

```bash
python InduceC45.py <dataset.csv> <output.json>
```

### 2. Make Predictions

```bash
python predict.py <dataset.csv> <tree.json> [eval]
```

---

### 3. Run Cross-Validation (Our Implementation)

```bash
python crossVal.py <dataset.csv> <params.json> [output_tree.json]
```


### 4. Run Cross-Validation (Scikit-learn)

```bash
python crossValSKL.py <dataset.csv> <params.json> <output_image.png>
```

## Dependencies


```bash
python -m pip install numpy pandas scikit-learn matplotlib
```

